data.title: Help
data.meta_description: help - Free ebook download as (.rtf), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document contains Telugu words for common nouns, verbs, adjectives, and other parts of speech along with their Telugu translations. There are over 200 entries covering a wide range of everyday vocabulary items from family members and body parts to foods, activities, weather, days of the week, numbers, and more.
